╬ú\t03A3\t931\tSummation (Uppercase)
¤â\t03C3\t963\tSigma (Lowercase)
Ôł×\t221E\t8734\tInfinity
Ôłź\t222B\t8747\tIntegral
ÔłÜ	221A	8730	Square Root
Ôëł	2248	8776	Almost Equal To
